column5: Flying into Joyce Lake early june 2011.....anyone have tips on pike/walleye at this lake? Hot spots/hot lures etc......I've caught big pike before just not at this lake....I'm not a walleye expert, however, & I'd like to catch enough to have some lunch....
fish right at the burn't white birch
I haven't fished it, but I know those who have and it's a great lake with very little pressure. C & R except for a few eaters while in camp. Should be great forever.
